                <h1>University partners with Durham architect to combat ALS</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/d3d780cd-1879-49ed-ba41-200c21a107c1.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Durham&#x20;architect&amp;nbsp&#x3B;Phil&#x20;Freelon&#x20;led&amp;nbsp&#x3B;the&#x20;design&#x20;team&#x20;for&#x20;the&#x20;Smithsonian&#x20;National&#x20;Museum&#x20;of&#x20;African&#x20;American&#x20;History&#x20;and&#x20;Culture&#x20;and&#x20;was&#x20;recently&#x20;diagnosed&#x20;with&#x20;ALS.&amp;nbsp&#x3B;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Durham architect&nbsp;Phil Freelon led&nbsp;the design team for the Smithsonian National Museum of African American History and Culture and was recently diagnosed with ALS.&nbsp;</p>

                            
                        </div>
                    </figure>
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/katherine-berko">Katherine Berko</a>
                                    
                                <div class="mt-1">
                                    <span class="can-localize">January 12, 2017 | 12:27am EST</span>
                                </div>
                            </aside>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-left text-md-right d-print-none">
                            <ul class="social-links list-unsyled list-inline mt-4 mt-md-0">
                                <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://www.dukechronicle.com/article/2017/01/university-partners-with-durham-architect-to-combat-als" target="_blank" class="sends-events" data-ga-category="Share" data-ga-action="click" data-ga-label="facebook" data-ga-value="CURL"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a></li>
